<figure typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/File:Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg/250px-Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="312" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg/375px-Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg/500px-Congregation_Emanu-El_of_the_City_New_York.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4049" data-file-height="5061" /></a><figcaption>The interior of <a href="/wiki/Congregation_Emanu-El_of_New_York" title="Congregation Emanu-El of New York">Congregation Emanu-El of New York</a>, the largest Reform <a href="/wiki/Synagogue" title="Synagogue">synagogue</a> in the world.</figcaption></figure>
